graph TB
    CC[Claude Code] -->|stdio JSON-RPC| STDIO[Stdio Transport]
    CD[Claude Desktop] -->|HTTP/HTTPS + OAuth| HTTP[HTTP Transport]

    STDIO --> MCP[MCP Server<br/>mark3labs/mcp-go]
    HTTP --> MW[Middleware Chain]
    MW --> MCP

    CD -->|OAuth flow| OAUTH[OAuth Provider<br/>Google / GitHub]
    OAUTH -->|token exchange| HTTP

    MCP --> GEN[generate_image]
    MCP --> EDIT[edit_image]
    MCP --> LIST[list_models]
    MCP --> REC[recommend_model]

    GEN --> SEC[Security Layer<br/>validate + sanitize]
    EDIT --> SEC
    LIST --> SEC
    REC --> POL[Policy Engine<br/>model recommendation]

    SEC --> RESOLVE{Resolve<br/>Gemini client}
    RESOLVE -->|default key| GCLIENT[Gemini Client<br/>google.golang.org/genai]
    RESOLVE -->|per-user key| CACHE[ClientCache<br/>per-user clients]

    GCLIENT -->|API Key| API[Google Gemini API]
    CACHE -->|X-Gemini-API-Key| API

    style SEC fill:#f9d,stroke:#333
    style MW fill:#bbf,stroke:#333
    style API fill:#bfb,stroke:#333
    style OAUTH fill:#ddf,stroke:#333
    style CACHE fill:#dfd,stroke:#333
